  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Oh hello there, dearie.</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(WARNING: This game includes flashing that may potentially trigger seizures for people with photosensitive epilepsy.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a little old lady who needs to clean your big magical cellar. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn colorful spells, meet strange NPCs, and uncover the secrets of the dungeon. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You die 100s of times and lose your memories in order to learn dark magic. it's cute!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876850/extras/1ff2bc9f3f92586e4a14cbc8b74c2f62.poster.avif?t=1770662259\" width=600 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876850/extras/1ff2bc9f3f92586e4a14cbc8b74c2f62.webm?t=1770662259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876850/extras/1ff2bc9f3f92586e4a14cbc8b74c2f62.mp4?t=1770662259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tidy up! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sweep away dust, monsters, bugs and more with your trusty broom.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn colorful hag magic that changes the rules of the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every creature has a unique mechanic!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the environment to solve puzzles and find secrets.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Free the elders trapped in the crystals. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purify the dungeon, purify the world.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be a Babushka!!!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your cat ran away! (she's a babushka too)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876850/extras/41d2e0a86bb194492380e03c10051f42.poster.avif?t=1770662259\" width=428 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876850/extras/41d2e0a86bb194492380e03c10051f42.webm?t=1770662259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876850/extras/41d2e0a86bb194492380e03c10051f42.mp4?t=1770662259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Oh hello there, dearie.</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(WARNING: This game includes flashing that may potentially trigger seizures for people with photosensitive epilepsy.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a little old lady who needs to clean your big magical cellar. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn colorful spells, meet strange NPCs, and uncover the secrets of the dungeon. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You die 100s of times and lose your memories in order to learn dark magic. it's cute!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876850/extras/1ff2bc9f3f92586e4a14cbc8b74c2f62.poster.avif?t=1770662259\" width=600 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876850/extras/1ff2bc9f3f92586e4a14cbc8b74c2f62.webm?t=1770662259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876850/extras/1ff2bc9f3f92586e4a14cbc8b74c2f62.mp4?t=1770662259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tidy up! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sweep away dust, monsters, bugs and more with your trusty broom.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn colorful hag magic that changes the rules of the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every creature has a unique mechanic!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the environment to solve puzzles and find secrets.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Free the elders trapped in the crystals. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purify the dungeon, purify the world.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be a Babushka!!!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your cat ran away! (she's a babushka too)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876850/extras/41d2e0a86bb194492380e03c10051f42.poster.avif?t=1770662259\" width=428 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876850/extras/41d2e0a86bb194492380e03c10051f42.webm?t=1770662259\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1876850/extras/41d2e0a86bb194492380e03c10051f42.mp4?t=1770662259\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
